mpany provides WIREFIT electrical conduit pipes and fittings and CABLEFIT cable ducting pipes; Hauraton surface drainage system; and Duratap polytetra methylene terepthalate tapware. Further, it offers bathware-faucets and showers, as well as sanitaryware. Prince Pipes and Fittings Limited was incorporated in 1987 and is headquartered in Mumbai, India."}}